to  reach  out  to  rural  America,  to  reach  out  to  retailers  to  partici-
pate  in  this  program,  not  just  big-box  retailers  and  large  nation-
wide chains, but also give us proposals on how they intend to reach 
out  to  rural  retailers  and  smaller  businesses.  We’ve  been  working 
with  the  Alaskan  Native  Broadcast  Corporation  and  Native  Voice 
