part  of  the  Commission’s  approach  to  this  has  been,  not  only  just 
developing the materials and making sure that we distribute them 
to  consumers  who  call,  or  consumers  who  write  us,  or  e-mail  us, 
but  making  sure  that  we  establish  partnerships  with  groups  all 

