adoption  of  new  technology  without  significant  problems  is  being 
shortsighted. 

But,  let  me  turn  to  Ms.  Seidel  for  a  second,  because  one  of  the 
other issues is about—you know, I think in our state we have four 
different  television  markets,  36  different  television  stations,  and 
