STATEMENT OF HON. JOHN THUNE, 
U.S. SENATOR FROM SOUTH DAKOTA 

Senator  THUNE.  And  they’re  all  watching  C–SPAN,  so  they’re 
going  to  make  sure  that  they’re  following  all  this  that  has  hap-
pened. So—— 
