provide  information  packets  to  70  councils  of  government,  local  development 
districts representing 23 million people in 410 counties (42 percent rural). 
• In  October,  NTIA  will  actively  participate  in  the  Rural  Telecommunications 
• NTIA has reached to the U.S. Department of Agriculture Cooperative State Re-
search, Education, and Extension Service to distribute information to extension 
offices nationwide. 

